Trade/Device Name(s): INNOVITA HCG Pregnancy Rapid Test Strip
INNOVITA HCG Pregnancy Rapid Test Cassette
INNOVITA HCG Pregnancy Rapid Test Midstream
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for INNOVITA HCG Pregnancy Rapid Test in strip, cassette, and midstream formats for visual, qualitative detection of hCG in urine for pregnancy determination
Indications for Use Summary: Detects human chorionic gonadotropin (hCG) in urine to obtain a visual, qualitative result for the determination of pregnancy; intended for over-the-counter, in vitro diagnostic use only
